sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant UI as UI Controller / ViewModel
    participant Dagger as Dagger
    participant Rhyme as RhymeAnalyzer
    participant Phoneme as PhonemeAnalyzer
    participant Cmu as CmuEngine
    participant Mary as MaryEngine
    participant Lazy as LazyService
    participant TaskBus as TaskBus
    participant Worker as Worker Thread

    UI->>Dagger: 1. Request injected RhymeAnalyzer

    Dagger->>Dagger: 2. Resolve RhymeAnalyzer dependencies

    Dagger->>Phoneme: 3. RhymeAnalyzer requires PhonemeAnalyzer

    Dagger->>Cmu: 4. PhonemeAnalyzer requires CmuEngine
    Dagger->>Cmu: 5. Construct CmuEngine
    Cmu->>Lazy: 6. Call LazyService constructor
    Lazy->>Lazy: 7. Call ensure()
    Lazy->>Lazy: 8. Check initialized == false
    Lazy->>TaskBus: 9. Submit "Starting CmuEngine"
    TaskBus->>TaskBus: 10. Queue initialization task
    TaskBus->>Worker: 11. Run CmuEngine.init() asynchronously

    Dagger->>Mary: 12. Construct MaryEngine
    Mary->>Lazy: 13. Call LazyService constructor
    Lazy->>TaskBus: 14. Submit "Starting MaryEngine"
    TaskBus->>TaskBus: 15. Queue initialization task
    TaskBus->>Worker: 16. Run MaryEngine.init() asynchronously

    Dagger->>Phoneme: 17. Construct PhonemeAnalyzer with CmuEngine and MaryEngine

    Dagger->>Rhyme: 18. Construct RhymeAnalyzer with PhonemeAnalyzer

    Dagger-->>UI: 19. Return injected RhymeAnalyzer

    Note over UI,Worker: 20. UI receives RhymeAnalyzer while expensive services initialize through TaskBus
